EDUCATIONAL PURPOSE DISCLAIMER:

This project is created SOLELY for educational purposes to demonstrate:
- Chrome Extension development (Manifest V3)
- Cookie-based authentication mechanisms
- Message passing between web applications and browser extensions
- Tab management and URL monitoring techniques

